<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <title>Welcome Admin</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      padding-top: 40px;
    }

    .image-container {
      width: 80%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: -5px 5px 20px rgba(210, 210, 210, 0.8);
    }

    .image-container img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .card {
      width: 400px;
      box-shadow: -10px 10px 25px rgba(210, 210, 210, .9);
      border-radius: 35px;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 50px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .card h2 {
      color: #20b2aa;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .card button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: #20b2aa;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1em;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    .card button:hover {
      background: #1a9a9a;
    }

    .card a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 10px 30px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: #20b2aa;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="image-container">
    <img src="/images/image.png" alt="Admin Banner">
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>于长夜重返大地</h2>
    <p>翁法罗斯三月•长夜月，长夜月现身，聪明的开拓者想让可爱的三月七回来，就得回溯到长夜月发布之前...</p>
    <p>「翁法罗斯的三月，是属于永夜之帷的时间…就以『长夜月』这个名字，来称呼这具化身——『她』的影子吧。」</p>
    <p>与世相隔的忆域，烛火映出过往，于迷雾中悄然熄去。
      自那影中而来的记忆之子长夜月，隐匿「岁月」火种的黄金裔，你要掀起「忘却」的浪潮，守护镜中人的心愿
      ——「别担心，我会为你看护『开拓』的前路…不惜任何代价♭」</p>

      <button id="submitBtn">提交有关长夜月的数据</button>


      <a href="/login">Logout</a>
    </div>
    <script>
      document.getElementById('submitBtn').addEventListener('click', async () => {
          const payload = {
              name: "EverNight",
              default_path: "The Remembrance",
              place: "Amphoreus",
              min_public_time: "2025-08-03"
          };
  
          try {
              const token = document.cookie.split('token=')[1]?.split(';')[0];
              const res = await fetch('/admin_club1st', {
                  method: 'POST',
                  headers: {
                      'Content-Type': 'application/json',
                      'Authorization': 'Bearer ' + token
                  },
                  body: JSON.stringify(payload)
              });
          } catch (err) {
              alert('Error: ' + err.message);
          }
      });
    </script>
</body>
</html>